news.title: Slum residents near JLN stadium in Delhi get eviction notice
news.para: On March 16, the officials sent the around 500 occupants of the 60 jhuggis an eviction notice. The residents of the slum, who have come to Delhi from West Bengal, Rajasthan and Bihar, have been asked to vacate the area before March 20.

news.title: Activists write to CM, centre opposing move to hand over Navi Mumbai wetlands for IT hub
news.para: Protesting against the project coming up on the "graves of mangroves and wetlands" of Uran, greens have said government-appointed site inspection committees have confirmed there will be destruction.

news.title: No sand extraction permits till May 17 in Goa: NGT
news.para: The final hearing in the sand extraction matter filed by the Goa River Sand Protectors Network will take place on that date.
